 (a) 128 nodes, 256 cpus Based on Sun Fire X2200 M2  (b) AMD 64 Opteron Dual Core 2.8 GHz within a node  (c) Total Memory 1024 GB  (e) Peak Performance 2+ Tflops  (f) Total Disk 42TB  (g) HSI: GbE 1Gbps links
 System Configuration:  (a) COS: base on Suse Linux 9.0 update 3
